{"content": "I need to multiply 462 \u00d7 633 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 462 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 462\u2081\u2081 = 4\u00d711\u00b2 + 6\u00d711\u00b9 + 2\u00d711\u2070\n- = 4\u00d7121 + 6\u00d711 + 2\u00d71\n- = 484 + 66 + 2\n- = 552\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 633 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 633\u2081\u2081 = 6\u00d711\u00b2 + 3\u00d711\u00b9 + 3\u00d711\u2070\n- = 6\u00d7121 + 3\u00d711 + 3\u00d71\n- = 726 + 33 + 3\n- = 762\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 552 \u00d7 762 = 420,624\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 420,624 back to base 11**\n- 420,624 \u00f7 11 = 38,238 R 6\n- 38,238 \u00f7 11 = 3,476 R 2\n- 3,476 \u00f7 11 = 316 R 0\n- 316 \u00f7 11 = 28 R 8\n- 28 \u00f7 11 = 2 R 6\n- 2 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 2\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 268026\n\n**Answer: 268026**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 396}